U.S. Aug. Small Business Authority Index: Summary

-- B y   A l e x   T a n z i
-- 
2011-09-23T14:37:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/u-s-aug-small-business-authority-index-summary-table-.html
The Small Business Authority index rose 
in August, according to NewTek Business Services Inc.  The Small Business Authority index strengthened to 108.1 in August
from 107.3 a month earlier. The index consists of several indicators 
that are weighted into an index of the small business economy. According
to Newtek, the index is highly correlated with GDP; with a correlation 
coefficient is .835.  SOURCE: Small Business Authority Index
www.thesba.com/2011/1/10/introducing-thesmall-
